### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### 1. Health Checks
GET http://localhost:3000/health
###
GET http://localhost:3000/live

### 2. Authentication

# Register an Admin User
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@assetflow.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "System",
  "lastName": "Admin"
}

###
# Login (Captures token for subsequent requests)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@assetflow.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Set the Auth Token Variable from the Login Response
@authToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### 3. Departments
# Create a Department (Requires Auth Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/departments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Engineering",
  "costCenter": "CC-ENG-01",
  "managerId": "{{login.response.body.data.user.id}}"
}

### Get All Departments
GET {{baseUrl}}/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
